ing v cc JS bundle c ti u ha."],["li",{},["strong",{},"Data-fetching utilities:"]," Nuxt cung cp cc composable  x l data fetching tng thch vi SSR cng nh cc chin lc khc nhau."],["li",{},["strong",{},"Zero-config TypeScript support:"]," vit code an ton kiu d liu m khng cn hc TypeScript vi cc type c t ng to v ",["code",{},"tsconfig.json"]," ca chng ti."],["li",{},["strong",{},"Configured build tools:"]," chng ti s dng ",["a",{"href":"https://vite.dev","rel":["nofollow"]},"Vite"]," theo mc nh  h tr hot module replacement (HMR) trong development v ng gi code cho production vi cc best-practice c tch hp sn."]],["p",{},"Nuxt x l tt c nhng iu ny v cung cp chc nng c frontend v backend  bn c th tp trung vo iu quan trng: ",["strong",{},"to ra ng dng web ca bn"],"."],["h2",{"id":"server-side-rendering"},"Server-Side Rendering"],["p",{},"Nuxt i km vi kh nng server-side rendering (SSR) tch hp sn theo mc nh, m khng cn phi t cu hnh server, iu ny mang li nhiu li ch cho cc ng dng web:"],["ul",{},["li",{},["strong",{},"Thi gian ti trang ban u nhanh hn:"]," Nuxt gi mt trang HTML c render y  n trnh duyt, c th c hin th ngay lp tc. iu ny c th cung cp thi gian ti trang nhanh hn v mt cm nhn v tri nghim ngi dng (UX) tt hn, c bit trn cc mng chm hoc thit b yu."],["li",{},["strong",{},"SEO c ci thin:"]," cc cng c tm kim c th index cc trang SSR tt hn v ni dung HTML c sn ngay lp tc, thay v yu cu JavaScript  render ni dung  pha client."],["li",{},["strong",{},"Hiu sut tt hn trn cc thit b yu:"]," n gim lng JavaScript cn c ti xung v thc thi  pha client, iu ny c th c li cho cc thit b yu c th gp kh khn khi x l cc ng dng JavaScript nng."],["li",{},["strong",{},"Kh nng truy cp tt hn:"]," ni dung c sn ngay lp tc khi ti trang ban u, ci thin kh nng truy cp cho ngi dng da vo screen reader hoc cc cng ngh h tr khc."],["li",{},["strong",{},"Caching d dng hn:"]," cc trang c th c cache  pha server, iu ny c th ci thin hiu sut hn na bng cch gim thi gian to v gi ni dung n client."]],["p",{},"Nhn chung, server-side rendering c th cung cp tri nghim ngi dng nhanh hn v hiu qu hn, cng nh ci thin ti u ha cng c tm kim v kh nng truy cp."],["p",{},"V Nuxt l mt framework linh hot, n cung cp cho bn kh nng render tnh ton b ng dng thnh static hosting vi ",["code",{},"nuxt generate"],", tt SSR ton cu vi ty chn ",["code",{},"ssr: false"]," hoc tn dng hybrid rendering bng cch thit lp ty chn ",["code",{},"routeRules"],"."],["read-more",{"title":"Nuxt rendering modes","to":"/docs/guide/concepts/rendering"}],["h3",{"id":"server-engine"},"Server engine"],["p",{},"Server engine Nuxt ",["a",{"href":"https://nitro.build/","rel":["nofollow"]},"Nitro"]," m kha cc kh nng full-stack mi."],["p",{},"Trong development, n s dng Rollup v Node.js workers cho server code v context isolation. N cng to server API ca bn bng cch c cc file trong ",["code",{},"server/api/"]," v server middleware t ",["code",{},"server/middleware/"],"."],["p",{},"Trong production, Nitro build ng dng v server ca bn thnh mt th mc ",["code",{},".output"]," universal duy nht. Output ny nh: c minify v loi b khi bt k Node.js module no (tr polyfill). Bn c th deploy output ny trn bt k h thng no h tr JavaScript, t Node.js, Serverless, Workers, Edge-side rendering hoc hon ton tnh."],["read-more",{"title":"Nuxt server engine","to":"/docs/guide/concepts/server-engine"}],["h3",{"id":"production-ready"},"Production-ready"],["p",{},"Mt ng dng Nuxt c th c deploy trn Node hoc Deno server, pre-render  c host trong mi trng tnh, hoc deploy n cc serverless v edge provider."],["read-more",{"title":"Deployment section","to":"/docs/getting-started/deployment"}],["h3",{"id":"modular"},"Modular"],["p",{},"H thng module cho php bn m rng Nuxt vi cc tnh nng ty chnh v tch hp vi cc dch v bn th ba."],["read-more",{"title":"Nuxt Modules Concept","to":"/docs/guide/concepts/modules"}],["h3",{"id":"architecture"},"Architecture"],["p",{},"Nuxt c cu to t cc ",["a",{"href":"https://github.com/nuxt/nuxt/tree/main/packages","rel":["nofollow"]},"core package"]," khc nhau:"],